name: SeekMIDI
tagline: SeekMIDI, a simple graphical multi-channel MIDI sequencer.
body:
### Welcome to SeekMIDI

SeekMIDI is a simple multi-channel MIDI sequencer for quick song creation. We'll post some screenshots here soon.

### How to get it

We recommend that if you have git experience, you clone the master. Because we're under fairly rapid development, the master will have the latest features.
